data.description: Welcome to your little piece of Valley Center! This house is close to all the schools and a prime spot for the big Valley Center Fall Festival parade that goes down Meridian every year! This home has just had a face lift with new paint, Wood floors redone and bathroom updated! This home is ready to go for its new owners!
